lead_paragraph: The Montreal Canadiens are already off to a strong start. It doesn't hurt that they have star goaltender Carey Price getting some early season rust off now, too.

headline.print_headline: Price Stops 19 Shots in 2nd Start, Canadiens Beat Bruins 4-2
